      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or imperfections, complemented by pristine alloy wheels with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear or creasing, still retaining that new-car scent. Every electronic feature, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history and an engine bay so meticulously maintained it appears untouched. This is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
